title: Google\Cloud\Build\V1\Artifacts\ArtifactObjects
name: ArtifactObjects
description:
Files in the workspace to upload to Cloud Storage upon successful completion of all build steps.

Generated from protobuf message google.devtools.cloudbuild.v1.Artifacts.ArtifactObjects

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.location
params.description: Cloud Storage bucket and optional object path, in the form "gs://bucket/path/to/somewhere/". (see Bucket Name Requirements). Files in the workspace matching any path pattern will be uploaded to Cloud Storage with this location as a prefix.

params.name: data.paths
params.description: Path globs used to match files in the build's workspace.

params.name: data.timing
params.description: Output only. Stores timing information for pushing all artifact objects.
